<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ṇṭu nicati Uḻakkeṇṇai Aṭṭuvippomāṉom Ērivāriyap perumakkaḷom I<hi rend="grantha">rddharmma</hi>m ra<hi rend="grantha">kṣi</hi>ppār <hi rend="grantha">ga</hi>ṅkaiyāṭinapalam
